
<h1>Question: <%= @question.steps_taken %></h1>
<h3>Asked by: <%= @name.name %></h3>

<h3>Expected Results: <%= @question.expected_results %></h3>
<h3>Actual Results: <%= @question.actual_results %></h3>
<h3>Link to my Code: <%= @question.code_link %></h3>
<h3>Question status: <%= @urgency.level %></h3>
<h3>Question resolved: <% if (@question.resolved == true)%>
                        YES</h3>
                        <% else %>NO</h3>
                        <% end%>
                      
<h3>Time Posted: <%= @question.created_at.localtime.strftime("%b %d at %l:%M") %></h3>

<p>If this is your question, you can click this link to edit the question.  Please mark it resolved once you have your answer!</p>

<p><a href="/questions/<%= @question.id %>/edit">Edit Your Question</a></p>
<p><a href="/questions">Go Back to all Questions</a></p>

<p><a href="/questions/<%= @question.id %>/comments/new">Add your answer here!</a></p>


 

